    "en": {
      "title": "Youth fell from bus and died",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 22-year-old youth named Nissanka Kumara Siri, who was traveling by bus from Kurupapila Kama area to Balangoda, slipped and fell from the bus.",
        "In Raskala area, the said youth slipped and fell while getting off the bus to spit."
